{"tid":1732863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好搞狗宿黎救理大","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T04:05:47.000Z","uid":330940,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a809b9fb86e5eb3232b2f840af64919941a8ac05","tid":1732863,"uid":330940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:35:08.000Z","msg":"宜家理大重狗到好似包圍恐怖分子咁 真係唔係咁易可以攻到入去救人<br />\n同埋如果理大入面手足真係無晒糧食 其實係咪可以搵有地位人士出面幫手出聲明比人圍困到無晒糧食 要求人道救援？<br />\n宜家各區手足要令到d狗覺得佢地圍理大係有代價 要取捨 要恐懼<br />\n大家係咪應該去狗宿探下佢地d屋企人同埋講佢地食下野飲下野？如果宜家唔去搵佢地 佢地收到風搬左去酒店到住就見佢地唔到嫁啦！<br />\n以上只係個人見解 唔岩聽就拉 我都好想救到手足<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人熱愛和平 唔鼓勵犯法"},{"pid":"ee69bd952a113261d6ad295168040933fc235d79","tid":1732863,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be19a1dc0a359fa6e719ac9cd67c1fe482b41dd9","tid":1732863,"uid":72381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"黑警FA都捉哂仲CARE人道？"},{"pid":"6dfc23001c241014824221b11e749381204375a6","tid":1732863,"uid":330940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be19a1dc0a359fa6e719ac9cd67c1fe482b41dd9","tid":1732863,"uid":72381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"黑警FA都捉哂仲CARE人道？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"人道唔係要班狗救 而係要求人道救援之後如果班狗拒絕 咁就可以製造國際輿論 等人地要用強硬手段幫手都出師有名d"},{"pid":"c60a0c22267e40c56ce75ce102a4421eab1d2daa","tid":1732863,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf0a28fa05d4a116c17caca583b7f247b8acf23","tid":1732863,"uid":293673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9fa67e74be5f23e81f4b56b9cffc0c9a819cfe6","tid":1732863,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/s